#. module: vehicle_rental
#: model:mail.template,body_html:vehicle_rental.scratch_report_review_signature_required_mail_template
msgid ""
"<h4>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.customer_id.name\"/>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    ,\n"
"                </h4>\n"
"                <hr style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0;\"/>\n"
"                <h4>\n"
"                    Greetings from\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"/>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                </h4>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    This email is regarding your recently completed rental contract\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.reference_no\"/>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    for the\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.vehicle_id.name\"/>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    .\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    During the return inspection, our team identified scratch damage on the vehicle. A detailed Scratch\n"
"                    Report has been prepared.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    To review the scratch details and provide your confirmation signature, please click the button\n"
"                    below:\n"
"                </p>\n"
"\n"
"                <a t-att-href=\"object.get_scratch_report_url()\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">\n"
"                    View &amp; Sign Scratch Report\n"
"                </a>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Kindly review the report carefully and submit your digital signature to complete the verification\n"
"                    process. This will allow us to proceed with the final settlement as per the rental agreement terms.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    If you have any questions or require clarification regarding the report, please contact us at your\n"
"                    convenience.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Thank you for your prompt cooperation.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0;\"/>\n"
"                <div>\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        Best regards,\n"
"                        <br/>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.responsible_id.name\"/>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.company_id.phone\"/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.company_id.email\"/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.company_id.website\"/>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"<h4>\n"
"                    Estimado\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"<t t-out=\"object.customer_id.name\"></t>\n"
"</strong>\n"
"                    ,\n"
"                </h4>\n"
"<hr style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0;\"/>\n"
"<h4>\n"
"                    saludos desde\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"<t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t>\n"
"</strong>\n"
"</h4>\n"
"<p>\n"
"                    Este correo electrónico se refiere a su contrato de alquiler recientemente completado.\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"<t t-out=\"object.reference_no\"></t>\n"
"</strong>\n"
"                    para el\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"<t t-out=\"object.vehicle_id.name\"></t>\n"
"</strong>\n"
"                    .\n"
"                </p>\n"
"<p>\n"
"                    Durante la inspección de devolución, nuestro equipo identificó daños por rayones en el vehículo. Un Scratch detallado\n"
"                    Se ha preparado el informe.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"<p>\n"
"                    Para revisar los detalles del scratch y proporcionar su firma de confirmación, haga clic en el botón\n"
"                    a continuación:\n"
"                </p>\n"
"<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" t-att-href=\"object.get_scratch_report_url()\" target=\"_blank\">\n"
"                    Ver y firmar el informe borrador\n"
"                </a>\n"
"<p>\n"
"                    Por favor revise el informe detenidamente y envíe su firma digital para completar la verificación.\n"
"                    proceso. Esto nos permitirá proceder con el acuerdo final según los términos del contrato de alquiler.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"<p>\n"
"                    Si tiene alguna pregunta o necesita una aclaración sobre el informe, comuníquese con nosotros a su\n"
"                    conveniencia.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"<p>\n"
"                    Gracias por su pronta cooperación.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"<hr style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0;\"/>\n"
"<div>\n"
"<strong>\n"
"                        Atentamente,\n"
"                        <br/>\n"
"<t t-out=\"object.responsible_id.name\"></t>\n"
"</strong>\n"
"<br/>\n"
"<t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t>\n"
"<br/>\n"
"<t t-out=\"object.company_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"<br/>\n"
"<t t-out=\"object.company_id.email\"></t>\n"
"<br/>\n"
"<t t-out=\"object.company_id.website\"></t>\n"
"</div>\n"

#. module: vehicle_rental
#: model:mail.template,body_html:vehicle_rental.vehicle_rental_booking_confirmation_mail_template
msgid ""
"<h4>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.customer_id.name\"/>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    ,\n"
"                </h4>\n"
"                <hr style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0;\"/>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Thank you for booking with\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"/>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    . Below are your rental details:\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr style=\"margin: 5px;\"/>\n"
"                <table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse;\">\n"
"                    <!-- Reference & Vehicle -->\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td style=\"width: 35%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"                            <strong>Reference No.</strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td style=\"width: 65%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"                            <span t-field=\"object.reference_no\"/>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td style=\"width: 35%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"                            <strong>Vehicle</strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td style=\"width: 65%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"                            <span t-field=\"object.vehicle_id.name\"/>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <!-- Pickup Section -->\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 100%; background-color:#f2f2f2; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"                            <strong>Pickup Details</strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td style=\"width: 35%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"                            <strong>Pickup Date</strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td style=\"width: 65%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"                            <span t-field=\"object.start_date\"/>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td style=\"vertical-align: middle; width: 35%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"                            <strong>Pickup Address</strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td style=\"width: 65%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"                            <t t-if=\"object.pick_up_street\">\n"
"                                <span t-field=\"object.pick_up_street\"/>\n"
"                                <br/>\n"
"                            </t>\n"
"                            <t t-if=\"object.pick_up_street2\">\n"
"                                <span t-field=\"object.pick_up_street2\"/>\n"
"                                <br/>\n"
"                            </t>\n"
"                            <t t-if=\"object.pick_up_city\">\n"
"                                <span t-field=\"object.pick_up_city\"/>\n"
"                                <span t-field=\"object.pick_up_state_id.name\"/>\n"
"                                <span t-field=\"object.pick_up_zip\"/>\n"
"                                <br/>\n"
"                            </t>\n"
"                            <t t-if=\"object.pick_up_country_id\">\n"
"                                <span t-field=\"object.pick_up_country_id.name\"/>\n"
"                            </t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <!-- Return Section -->\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 100%; background-color:#f2f2f2; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"                            <strong>Return Details</strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td style=\"width: 35%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"                            <strong>Drop-off Date</strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td style=\"width: 65%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"                            <span t-field=\"object.end_date\"/>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td style=\"vertical-align: middle; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"                            <strong>Drop-off Address</strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td style=\"width: 65%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"                            <t t-if=\"object.drop_off_street\">\n"
"                                <span t-field=\"object.drop_off_street\"/>\n"
"                                <br/>\n"
"                            </t>\n"
"                            <t t-if=\"object.drop_off_street2\">\n"
"                                <span t-field=\"object.drop_off_street2\"/>\n"
"                                <br/>\n"
"                            </t>\n"
"                            <t t-if=\"object.drop_off_city\">\n"
"                                <span t-field=\"object.drop_off_city\"/>\n"
"                                <span t-field=\"object.drop_off_state_id.name\"/>\n"
"                                <span t-field=\"object.drop_off_zip\"/>\n"
"                                <br/>\n"
"                            </t>\n"
"                            <t t-if=\"object.drop_off_country_id\">\n"
"                                <span t-field=\"object.drop_off_country_id.name\"/>\n"
"                            </t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                </table>\n"
"                <hr style=\"margin: 5px;\"/>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Please be available at the pickup location on time and carry your required documents.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    For any support or changes, feel free to contact us.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Have a great trip!\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0;\"/>\n"
"                <span>\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        Best regards,\n"
"                        <br/>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.responsible_id.name\"/>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.company_id.phone\"/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.company_id.email\"/>\n"
"                    <br/>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.company_id.website\"/>\n"
"                </span>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"<h4>\n"
"                    Estimado\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"<t t-out=\"object.customer_id.name\"></t>\n"
"</strong>\n"
"                    ,\n"
"                </h4>\n"
"<hr style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0;\"/>\n"
"<p>\n"
"                    Gracias por reservar con\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"<t t-out=\"object.company_id.name\"></t>\n"
"</strong>\n"
"                    . A continuación se muestran los detalles de su alquiler:\n"
"                </p>\n"
"<hr style=\"margin: 5px;\"/>\n"
"<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse;\">\n"
" Referencia y vehículo \n"
"<tr>\n"
"<td style=\"width: 35%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"<strong>Número de referencia.</strong>\n"
"</td>\n"
"<td style=\"width: 65%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.reference_no\"></span>\n"
"</td>\n"
"</tr>\n"
"<tr>\n"
"<td style=\"width: 35%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"<strong>Vehículo</strong>\n"
"</td>\n"
"<td style=\"width: 65%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.vehicle_id.name\"></span>\n"
"</td>\n"
"</tr>\n"
" Sección de recogida \n"
"<tr>\n"
"<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 100%; background-color:#f2f2f2; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"<strong>Detalles de recogida</strong>\n"
"</td>\n"
"</tr>\n"
"<tr>\n"
"<td style=\"width: 35%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"<strong>Fecha de recogida</strong>\n"
"</td>\n"
"<td style=\"width: 65%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.start_date\"></span>\n"
"</td>\n"
"</tr>\n"
"<tr>\n"
"<td style=\"vertical-align: middle; width: 35%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"<strong>Dirección de recogida</strong>\n"
"</td>\n"
"<td style=\"width: 65%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"<t t-if=\"object.pick_up_street\">\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.pick_up_street\"></span>\n"
"<br/>\n"
"</t>\n"
"<t t-if=\"object.pick_up_street2\">\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.pick_up_street2\"></span>\n"
"<br/>\n"
"</t>\n"
"<t t-if=\"object.pick_up_city\">\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.pick_up_city\"></span>\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.pick_up_state_id.name\"></span>\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.pick_up_zip\"></span>\n"
"<br/>\n"
"</t>\n"
"<t t-if=\"object.pick_up_country_id\">\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.pick_up_country_id.name\"></span>\n"
"</t>\n"
"</td>\n"
"</tr>\n"
" Sección de devolución \n"
"<tr>\n"
"<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 100%; background-color:#f2f2f2; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"<strong>Detalles de devolución</strong>\n"
"</td>\n"
"</tr>\n"
"<tr>\n"
"<td style=\"width: 35%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"<strong>Fecha de entrega</strong>\n"
"</td>\n"
"<td style=\"width: 65%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.end_date\"></span>\n"
"</td>\n"
"</tr>\n"
"<tr>\n"
"<td style=\"vertical-align: middle; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"<strong>Dirección de entrega</strong>\n"
"</td>\n"
"<td style=\"width: 65%; padding: 5px;\">\n"
"<t t-if=\"object.drop_off_street\">\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.drop_off_street\"></span>\n"
"<br/>\n"
"</t>\n"
"<t t-if=\"object.drop_off_street2\">\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.drop_off_street2\"></span>\n"
"<br/>\n"
"</t>\n"
"<t t-if=\"object.drop_off_city\">\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.drop_off_city\"></span>\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.drop_off_state_id.name\"></span>\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.drop_off_zip\"></span>\n"
"<br/>\n"
"</t>\n"
"<t t-if=\"object.drop_off_country_id\">\n"
"<span t-field=\"object.drop_off_country_id.name\"></span>\n"
"</t>\n"
"</td>\n"
"</tr>\n"
"</table>\n"
"<hr style=\"margin: 5px;\"/>\n"
"<p>\n"
"                    Esté disponible a tiempo en el lugar de recogida y lleve los documentos requeridos.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"<p>\n"
"                    Para cualquier soporte o cambio, no dude en contactarnos.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"<p>\n"
